Paper: hep-th/9312126

Date: 1993-12-14

Title: Cayley-Klein Algebras as Graded Contractions of so(N+1)

Authors: F.J. Herranz, M. de Montigny, M.A. del Olmo and M. Santander

Comments: 13 pages, Preprint UVA, AMS-TeX

We study $\Bbb Z_2^{\otimes N}$ graded contractions of the real compactsimple Lie algebra $so(N+1)$, and we identify within them the Cayley-Kleinalgebras as a naturally distinguished subset.